Version 0.01_01 (March 26, 2008)
  - initial developmental version, starting from PPM-2.1.8
  - apply patch from sisyphus:
      http://rt.cpan.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=28794
    to handle zip files from repositories
  - apply patch:
      http://rt.cpan.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=34084
    to append correct "-5.10" to architecture string for perl-5.10
  - various fixes so that the parsing of ppd files doesn't choke
    on REQUIRE or PROVIDE elements
  - populate ppm.xml with available repository information
    appropriate for the perl version
  - remove requirement of SOAP::Lite for perl-5.10, as repositories
    for this version are summary-file based, not soap-based
  - refuse to install if a ppm.bat is found under 